00:23:03,450 --> 00:23:06,890
(A car arrives at the coffee shop where the younger men are waiting.)

543
00:23:08,320 --> 00:23:09,690
I think...

544
00:23:09,990 --> 00:23:12,359
I'm the total package.

545
00:23:12,360 --> 00:23:13,529
(I think I'm the total package.)

546
00:23:13,530 --> 00:23:15,500
In terms of intelligence, personality,

547
00:23:15,530 --> 00:23:17,599
and looks, I lack nothing.

548
00:23:17,600 --> 00:23:18,700
She has it all?

549
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:20,769
I've already bought a house...

550
00:23:20,770 --> 00:23:22,840
at the best location in all of South Korea.

551
00:23:22,870 --> 00:23:24,410
That's amazing.

552
00:23:24,440 --> 00:23:26,240
He can just stay at home and be a homemaker.

553
00:23:26,780 --> 00:23:27,910
I'll be the breadwinner.

554
00:23:29,080 --> 00:23:31,850
I could pay off his student loan.

555
00:23:32,010 --> 00:23:34,520
But I won't be able to tolerate...

556
00:23:34,650 --> 00:23:35,920
any credit loans.

557
00:23:36,650 --> 00:23:39,020
I'm confident...

558
00:23:39,290 --> 00:23:41,620
that they'll fall for me eventually.

559
00:23:42,890 --> 00:23:43,989
(Lee Jin Young)

560
00:23:43,990 --> 00:23:45,589
Oh, she's pretty.

561
00:23:45,590 --> 00:23:47,400
(Lee Jin Young)

562
00:23:47,800 --> 00:23:50,830
(The fifth older woman walks toward the younger men.)

563
00:23:53,070 --> 00:23:54,240
Hello.

564
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:56,000
Hi, everyone.

565
00:23:57,970 --> 00:23:59,140
Wake up, Jin Wu.

566
00:23:59,940 --> 00:24:01,310
Wake up, dude!

567
00:24:02,380 --> 00:24:04,449
Oh, my gosh.

568
00:24:04,450 --> 00:24:06,110
Hi, everyone.

569
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:12,650
(They don't know where to look as soon as she enters.)

570
00:24:13,760 --> 00:24:15,490
Jun Han seems to be in love.

571
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:17,989
- Hello. - Hello.

572
00:24:17,990 --> 00:24:20,300
(They weren't expecting to see her.)

573
00:24:20,660 --> 00:24:22,160
We should get her a chair.

574
00:24:25,600 --> 00:24:27,940
Jin Wu is the first one to move.

575
00:24:28,270 --> 00:24:29,469
You can sit in the top seat.

576
00:24:29,470 --> 00:24:31,040
(Jin Wu moves faster than any other men.)

577
00:24:31,770 --> 00:24:34,240
(Restless)

578
00:24:35,080 --> 00:24:36,550
They're all stunned.

579
00:24:37,450 --> 00:24:39,410
- Hello. - It's nice to meet you all.

580
00:24:39,450 --> 00:24:40,919
- Nice to meet you. - Hi.

581
00:24:40,920 --> 00:24:42,050
Hello.

582
00:24:42,780 --> 00:24:44,150
Have you been waiting long?

583
00:24:45,820 --> 00:24:47,560
- No, not really. - No?

584
00:24:47,720 --> 00:24:49,390
- That's good. - If we had known you were coming,

585
00:24:49,460 --> 00:24:51,530
we would have dressed up more.

586
00:24:51,590 --> 00:24:53,630
- Didn't you know I was coming? - Not at all.

587
00:24:54,900 --> 00:24:57,170
Really? I see.

588
00:24:59,130 --> 00:25:01,670
(Looking)

589
00:25:02,270 --> 00:25:04,740
She looked fancy.

590
00:25:05,740 --> 00:25:07,979
Appearance-wise, I like women...

591
00:25:07,980 --> 00:25:09,909
who have large eyes...

592
00:25:09,910 --> 00:25:11,580
like a fennec fox.

593
00:25:12,180 --> 00:25:14,149
She was beautiful.

594
00:25:14,150 --> 00:25:16,120
(She was beautiful.)

595
00:25:21,260 --> 00:25:22,719
All the younger men are frozen...

596
00:25:22,720 --> 00:25:24,629
- because she looked so tough. - Yes.

597
00:25:24,630 --> 00:25:26,190
- They don't know what to do. - Exactly.

598
00:25:26,260 --> 00:25:27,330
It's cute.

599
00:25:28,800 --> 00:25:30,370
Tell me your names, please.

600
00:25:30,930 --> 00:25:32,870
I'm Yu Jin Wu.

601
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:35,470
- Yu Jin Wu. - Jin Wu.

602
00:25:36,070 --> 00:25:37,710
I'm Lee Si Won.

603
00:25:38,410 --> 00:25:39,740
Lee Si Won.

604
00:25:40,540 --> 00:25:42,180
I'm Lee Yun So.

605
00:25:42,510 --> 00:25:44,049
- Lee Yun... - So.

606
00:25:44,050 --> 00:25:45,350
- Yun So. - Yes.

607
00:25:45,480 --> 00:25:47,379
- I'm Lee Jun Han. - Jun Han.

608
00:25:47,380 --> 00:25:48,550
- Yes, Jun Han. - Jun Han.

609
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:50,819
My name is Lee Jin Young.

610
00:25:50,820 --> 00:25:52,150
- Please remember. - We will.

611
00:25:52,750 --> 00:25:53,820
Jin Young?

612
00:25:55,990 --> 00:25:57,590
- Lee Jin Young. - Jin Young.

613
00:25:57,790 --> 00:25:58,790
Jin Young.

614
00:25:59,760 --> 00:26:02,200
Have you gotten to know each other by now?

615
00:26:02,730 --> 00:26:03,869
- The men did. - Considering it's our first...

616
00:26:03,870 --> 00:26:05,130
Just the men?

617
00:26:05,470 --> 00:26:06,940
What about the women?

618
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:08,740
- We're getting to know them. - We're pretty close.

619
00:26:10,040 --> 00:26:12,710
I see. I was worried, in fact.

620
00:26:13,070 --> 00:26:14,709
I was worried that you would all be close by now.

621
00:26:14,710 --> 00:26:16,279
Of course, she was.

622
00:26:16,280 --> 00:26:18,810
We only met last night, so...

623
00:26:19,380 --> 00:26:20,919
- Last night? - Yes.

624
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:22,179
(Relieved)

625
00:26:22,180 --> 00:26:23,349
I see.

626
00:26:23,350 --> 00:26:24,820
- What would you like? - What would you like?

627
00:26:24,890 --> 00:26:26,020
I...

628
00:26:26,420 --> 00:26:28,919
I'll take the orange drink.

629
00:26:28,920 --> 00:26:30,660
- Orange? - Yes, please.

630
00:26:31,890 --> 00:26:33,329
(Jin Wu naturally looks after her.)

631
00:26:33,330 --> 00:26:35,530
Jin Wu is so sweet.

632
00:26:35,630 --> 00:26:37,329
- You all had lunch, right? - Yes.

633
00:26:37,330 --> 00:26:38,499
- Didn't you? - Me?

634
00:26:38,500 --> 00:26:39,670
- No. - Should we give you bread?

635
00:26:39,700 --> 00:26:41,340
I feel like we should give her bread.

636
00:26:41,900 --> 00:26:42,900
Do you want me to cut it?

637
00:26:43,310 --> 00:26:44,640
- The cake? - Yes.

638
00:26:44,670 --> 00:26:45,969
- This is... - Would you like a fork?

639
00:26:45,970 --> 00:26:47,440
Thank you.

640
00:26:47,680 --> 00:26:49,609
(The younger men got busy looking after her.)

641
00:26:49,610 --> 00:26:50,810
Do you like it?

642
00:26:51,080 --> 00:26:52,250
Eat up.

643
00:26:52,880 --> 00:26:54,050
You can eat.

644
00:26:55,450 --> 00:26:58,150
(Staring)

645
00:27:01,260 --> 00:27:03,230
Would you like a blanket if it's uncomfortable?

646
00:27:04,630 --> 00:27:05,690
Yes, please.

647
00:27:06,390 --> 00:27:07,799
- That was so sweet. - I was about to ask you.

648
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:08,960
You're so considerate.

649
00:27:09,030 --> 00:27:10,600
I was about to ask you.

650
00:27:11,470 --> 00:27:12,970
You're amazing.

651
00:27:14,570 --> 00:27:18,640
(They were one step behind.)

652
00:27:19,540 --> 00:27:21,440
Jin Wu is so sweet.

653
00:27:21,610 --> 00:27:22,980
Thank you.

654
00:27:24,850 --> 00:27:26,110
(Smiling)

655
00:27:28,950 --> 00:27:30,890
I'm so thankful.

656
00:27:30,950 --> 00:27:33,259
I don't know if he's always that considerate,

657
00:27:33,260 --> 00:27:34,289
but he is.

658
00:27:34,290 --> 00:27:36,120
- He's so polite. - It's natural for him.

659
00:27:36,190 --> 00:27:37,560
Does that give him extra points?

660
00:27:37,830 --> 00:27:40,130
I'd be so grateful. He does get extra points.

661
00:27:40,160 --> 00:27:41,659
A sweet guy is the best.

662
00:27:41,660 --> 00:27:43,029
- Yes, a sweet guy. - Yes.

663
00:27:43,030 --> 00:27:44,900
Did you do anything before this?

664
00:27:44,930 --> 00:27:46,029
- We... - Were you on a date?

665
00:27:46,030 --> 00:27:47,600
- Yes, we all were. - Yes.

666
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:50,410
I have a question, then.

667
00:27:50,540 --> 00:27:53,740
Do you have anyone you're interested in?

668
00:27:54,610 --> 00:27:55,640
All of you.

669
00:27:56,310 --> 00:27:58,349
How would they answer that?

670
00:27:58,350 --> 00:27:59,779
(She asked them out of the blue.)

671
00:27:59,780 --> 00:28:01,280
(Flustered)

672
00:28:02,180 --> 00:28:04,690
We had a vote on the first night, so...

673
00:28:04,890 --> 00:28:07,160
I'm sure everyone has one.

674
00:28:07,420 --> 00:28:08,859
That was a good save, Yun So.

675
00:28:08,860 --> 00:28:09,929
You must be worried.

676
00:28:09,930 --> 00:28:11,160
- Me? - Right?

677
00:28:11,990 --> 00:28:13,999
No, I'm not worried.

678
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:15,630
(No, I'm not worried)

679
00:28:18,130 --> 00:28:19,270
I'm not.

680
00:28:20,040 --> 00:28:22,000
I doubt anything major happened in only one day.

681
00:28:22,600 --> 00:28:23,609
That's true.

682
00:28:23,610 --> 00:28:24,969
- Am I right? - Yes.

683
00:28:24,970 --> 00:28:26,010
Right.

684
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:28,480
Do you have a type, Jin Young?

685
00:28:30,950 --> 00:28:32,279
I actually...

686
00:28:32,280 --> 00:28:36,790
(What's her ideal type?)

687
00:28:40,360 --> 00:28:42,519
I like someone who's like a puppy.

688
00:28:42,520 --> 00:28:43,559
A puppy?

689
00:28:43,560 --> 00:28:45,229
Like a large dog?

690
00:28:45,230 --> 00:28:46,859
Like...

691
00:28:46,860 --> 00:28:48,329
- Maltese? - A large...

692
00:28:48,330 --> 00:28:49,560
Not a Maltese.

693
00:28:50,230 --> 00:28:52,399
(Joking)

694
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:55,240
I like someone who's like a large dog,

695
00:28:55,770 --> 00:28:59,169
but when I think about everyone I've dated so far,

696
00:28:59,170 --> 00:29:00,909
they were all different.

697
00:29:00,910 --> 00:29:02,309
I don't think...

698
00:29:02,310 --> 00:29:05,080
it's about the looks. Once I'm hooked on something,

699
00:29:05,780 --> 00:29:07,080
I fall for him.

700
00:29:07,920 --> 00:29:10,450
- Is there a specific quality? - Specific?

701
00:29:11,020 --> 00:29:12,219
When he's...

702
00:29:12,220 --> 00:29:13,360
being considerate?

703
00:29:13,390 --> 00:29:15,290
- Considerate. - Considerate.

704
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:17,690
Jin Wu must have earned a few points.

705
00:29:18,330 --> 00:29:19,459
Jin Wu must have earned a few points.

706
00:29:19,460 --> 00:29:20,599
I know, right?

707
00:29:20,600 --> 00:29:21,700
The blanket.

708
00:29:22,160 --> 00:29:23,969
Jin Wu!

709
00:29:23,970 --> 00:29:25,030
(Shy)

710
00:29:26,370 --> 00:29:27,800
You can't beat sweetness.

711
00:29:28,770 --> 00:29:30,710
And I'd like to have good banter.

712
00:29:31,570 --> 00:29:33,510
- Like... - Do you like to make jokes?

713
00:29:34,540 --> 00:29:36,680
- You're trying to make jokes. - No.

714
00:29:37,010 --> 00:29:38,379
I like it, though.

715
00:29:38,380 --> 00:29:40,180
I like a guy who's funny...

716
00:29:40,380 --> 00:29:42,050
and is on the same wavelength.

717
00:29:42,420 --> 00:29:45,490
Being able to have a proper conversation.

718
00:29:45,750 --> 00:29:47,890
It's all good as long as we have fun together.

719
00:29:48,660 --> 00:29:49,860
Have you dated a younger guy before?

720
00:29:51,530 --> 00:29:54,430
No. Never.

721
00:29:54,730 --> 00:29:56,460
I've never even dated anyone my age.

722
00:29:57,870 --> 00:30:00,300
- How young can you tolerate? - How young?

723
00:30:01,300 --> 00:30:03,340
- Five or six years? - Five or six?

724
00:30:03,540 --> 00:30:04,555
Five or six years?

725
00:30:06,610 --> 00:30:10,080
Say you had feelings for someone without knowing his age.

726
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:12,310
Then, you found out he was more than five years younger.

727
00:30:12,910 --> 00:30:15,050
- Would you have a change of heart? - No, I don't think so.

728
00:30:15,520 --> 00:30:16,620
She's honest.

729
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:18,219
Age doesn't really matter to you.

730
00:30:18,220 --> 00:30:19,750
- No. - The person matters more.

731
00:30:20,260 --> 00:30:21,660
You're really sociable.

732
00:30:22,220 --> 00:30:23,220
- Me? - Yes.

733
00:30:23,221 --> 00:30:24,889
- I'm trying. - You're trying.

734
00:30:24,890 --> 00:30:26,429
- I'm trying. - You're so unfazed...

735
00:30:26,430 --> 00:30:27,430
in front of four men.

736
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:30,400
Well, I'm older than all of you.

737
00:30:30,770 --> 00:30:33,200
I have to do something, right?

738
00:30:34,300 --> 00:30:36,400
(He finds her cute.)

739
00:30:37,410 --> 00:30:39,270
(Smiling brightly)

740
00:30:39,510 --> 00:30:40,680
I'm older, after all.

741
00:30:42,280 --> 00:30:44,350
I have a feeling you have a lot of cute charms.

742
00:30:44,380 --> 00:30:45,480
- Cute charms? - Yes.

743
00:30:46,410 --> 00:30:47,880
- Does it look like I do? - Yes.

744
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:51,290
You're not going to answer that?

745
00:30:52,990 --> 00:30:55,559
You can try and be closer if you're curious.

746
00:30:55,560 --> 00:30:57,759
(You can try and be closer if you're curious.)

747
00:30:57,760 --> 00:30:59,230
Jin Young knows how to ease things off.

748
00:30:59,890 --> 00:31:02,100
(Glancing)

749
00:31:02,760 --> 00:31:04,270
(Glancing)

750
00:31:04,930 --> 00:31:07,600
The younger men met a new older woman.

751
00:31:08,070 --> 00:31:10,209
Is that a positive reaction? Do you think they're excited?

752
00:31:10,210 --> 00:31:12,239
I'd say it's super positive.

753
00:31:12,240 --> 00:31:13,269
- Super positive? - Super positive?

754
00:31:13,270 --> 00:31:15,310
But they've said things before she got there,

755
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:17,949
so they're trying to keep their dignity.

756
00:31:17,950 --> 00:31:19,049
- Oh, my gosh. - I see.

757
00:31:19,050 --> 00:31:20,980
But the women were the same.

758
00:31:21,180 --> 00:31:22,619
They told each other...

759
00:31:22,620 --> 00:31:25,049
- about how nice the dates were. - No, that's different.

760
00:31:25,050 --> 00:31:28,090
The women forgot about everything the moment Jeong Won walked in.

761
00:31:28,460 --> 00:31:29,759
But the guys remember what they said,

762
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:31,459
so they're trying to keep their pride.

763
00:31:31,460 --> 00:31:33,700
I noticed that they were pretending.

764
00:31:36,100 --> 00:31:37,370
Was that too obvious?

765
00:31:38,070 --> 00:31:39,400
I think you got a text.

766
00:31:40,340 --> 00:31:41,440
She got a message.

767
00:31:45,210 --> 00:31:46,569
(Take the hand of the younger man you're attracted to, go outside,)

768
00:31:46,570 --> 00:31:47,909
(and enjoy your 1-on-1 date.)

769
00:31:47,910 --> 00:31:49,880
- Are you flustered? - I am.

770
00:31:50,610 --> 00:31:51,950
It's too sudden.

771
00:31:52,710 --> 00:31:54,779
(They don't know what the message is about,)

772
00:31:54,780 --> 00:31:59,849
(but they're nervous for some reason.)

773
00:31:59,850 --> 00:32:01,860
I personally like Jin Wu and Jin Young together.

774
00:32:02,420 --> 00:32:04,790
I'm rooting for those two.

775
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:07,760
But Si Won makes a lasting first impression.

776
00:32:07,930 --> 00:32:10,170
He does. He's good-looking.

777
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:16,570
To be honest, I was torn between Jun Han and Jin Wu.

778
00:32:17,870 --> 00:32:19,110
Okay.

779
00:32:19,510 --> 00:32:22,580
Jin Wu was so handsome when I saw him.

780
00:32:22,780 --> 00:32:24,010
He stood out.

781
00:32:25,280 --> 00:32:27,620
He was too handsome to look at.

782
00:32:28,550 --> 00:32:30,650
I actually had a hard time looking him in the eye.

783
00:32:31,750 --> 00:32:35,389
Jun Han was quick to react,

784
00:32:35,390 --> 00:32:36,929
and he was funny.

785
00:32:36,930 --> 00:32:39,030
He felt like a good friend I felt comfortable to be with.

786
00:32:40,160 --> 00:32:42,730
I couldn't decide...

787
00:32:42,830 --> 00:32:48,339
between someone who I was more interested in...

788
00:32:48,340 --> 00:32:51,370
and someone who could have a good time with me.

789
00:32:51,870 --> 00:32:53,609
(Who will she ask out?)

790
00:32:53,610 --> 00:32:54,680
She's thinking.

791
00:32:54,780 --> 00:32:55,763
The weather's nice.

792
00:32:56,040 --> 00:32:57,810
Do you want to go on a date with me, Jun Han?

793
00:32:58,680 --> 00:33:00,619
(The younger man she wants to go on a date with...)

794
00:33:00,620 --> 00:33:02,320
(is Jun Han.)

795
00:33:04,190 --> 00:33:05,190
Sure.

796
00:33:05,850 --> 00:33:06,990
- See you. - Come on.

797
00:33:09,160 --> 00:33:10,189
We'll be back.

798
00:33:10,190 --> 00:33:11,190
Come on.

799
00:33:17,170 --> 00:33:19,070
Over there. We have to hold hands.

800
00:33:19,270 --> 00:33:20,340
We do?

801
00:33:22,040 --> 00:33:23,199
Let's go on a date.

802
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:25,840
(Jin Young and Jun Han go on a date while holding hands.)

803
00:33:26,240 --> 00:33:29,109
Jin Young and Jun Han look compatible, personality-wise.

804
00:33:29,110 --> 00:33:30,509
- Yes. - I agree.

805
00:33:30,510 --> 00:33:31,680
(Excited about their date)

806
00:33:32,210 --> 00:33:37,949
(And the younger men who weren't chosen)

807
00:33:37,950 --> 00:33:39,689
I wonder who the male catfish is.

808
00:33:39,690 --> 00:33:41,320
Right. So do I.

809
00:33:42,490 --> 00:33:44,660
He must have gone on a date with one of the women, then.

810
00:33:45,690 --> 00:33:48,660
We'll be able to find out who he took when we get there.

811
00:33:48,860 --> 00:33:51,429
We probably will, right?

812
00:33:51,430 --> 00:33:52,470
Yes.

813
00:33:53,570 --> 00:33:55,139
